          "text": "aspnet_Membership_GetUserByName",
          "marks": [
            {
              "type": "code"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "type": "text",
          "text": " is designed to retrieve user information from a membership system based on the application name and username. It optionally updates the user's last activity date. The procedure interacts with tables related to applications, users, and membership details, and it also checks an additional membership table for user activity status."
        }
